{"tid":10732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"表叔姪女烹貓屍餵狗罰款一千　官：香港與大陸不同","createTime":"2016-11-29T05:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T07:41:43.000Z","uid":4942,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f1c8d704ab522e9da0d68ce6713f7c35a10de39","tid":10732,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:10:27.000Z","msg":"一對表叔姪女在八鄉村屋外將一隻貓屍勾在木梯上，再分工用火槍和刀除淨貓毛，預備烹煮貓屍，巡邏警員見狀即拘捕兩人。表叔早前已認罪，持雙程證來港的姪女原本不認罪，案件原定今（29日）天在屯門法院開審，惟她改口認罪。<br />\n<br />\n姪女求情時透露，當時心想「食得唔好嘥，諗住比狗食」。裁判官水佳麗判刑時指「香港與大陸不同，動物在香港受到保護，可能在中國無呢個保護」，又強調香港法例不容許進食死去的動物，並特別告誡被告，「如果要來香港生活，就要明白、理解及尊重呢度嘅法例，以此為鑑」。<br />\n<br />\n報稱工廠工人的表叔唐勛光（53歲）早前已承認一項使用貓肉作食物罪。而侄女舒興巧（37歲）早前表明不認罪，惟今突改口同承認一項使用貓肉作食物罪，各被罰款1000元。舒離開法庭時，因不滿傳媒拍攝而破口大罵，為避開鏡頭，更一度欲爬上圍欄橫過馬路，惟遭男途人喝止。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">裁判官水佳麗判刑時表示，「大概呢個（進食動物）係香港及大陸嘅分別，（香港）對貓同狗仍然好尊重」</span>，水官強調動物在香港受到保護，「但可能在中國無呢個價值觀，好多嘢都食得，正如你（被告）講「唔係人食，就比狗食」。"},{"pid":"9bbab01ce9a6a9bb99a140ab70ac8826603c3998","tid":10732,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:11:14.000Z","msg":"水官續稱，貓狗是人類的朋友，香港亦有貓狗條例保護，對寵物好尊重，「呢個就係香港精神」，「唔容許死咗，就可以食」，又告誡兩被告稱，「如果要來香港生活，就要明白、理解、尊重呢度嘅法例，以此為鑑」，又指香港與大陸不同，即使瀕臨絕種動物、奇珍異獸也不能進食，並敦促兩被告要以此為鑑。<br />\n<br />\n抱「食得唔好嘥」的想法 　一心想將貓兒「俾狗食」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">首被告舒興巧的代表律師求情時指，持雙程證來港的她與67歲的港人丈夫育有一名14歲女兒，女兒患有過度活躍症。她曾於2002年因違反逗留條件而留有案底。</span>案中的貓兒為流浪貓，首被告會用廚餘餵貓的習慣，而貓兒亦視首被告為主人。首被告某日發現貓兒疑凍死，因愚昧及抱「食得唔好嘥」的想法，一心想將貓兒「俾狗食」，但因不熟悉香港法例而犯案，並保證不會重犯。"},{"pid":"d09e41e6d53f23c402b10f9168c7c8216b49bcd5","tid":10732,"uid":26076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7767961d8d3678eb60932630f33b0c07499055f1","tid":10732,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:23:14.000Z","msg":"首被告某日發現貓兒疑凍死，因愚昧及抱「食得唔好嘥」的想法，一心想將貓兒「俾狗食」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce434f8e51f9fe34c2c4d08bc6ae5f8f95ada030","tid":10732,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:23:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73b361ba1f88e2bc99bdadc51440d7437ea521b7","tid":10732,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:23:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哈哈，我以前喺廣東省江門市食過貓肉狗肉同蛇肉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返江門啦你"},{"pid":"03d6c265a97a0f6104ad129262525ae376daa7e1","tid":10732,"uid":1577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:26:15.000Z","msg":"水官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次聽人姓水"},{"pid":"6f69de13680219c62cf4ffacabe82915d94d7a10","tid":10732,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:31:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d39b18144d56d5f0dc003eb96d75bb1a210ee5c6","tid":10732,"uid":19191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老實講，狗肉同蛇肉的味道已經唔記得，畢竟好耐之前<br />\n<br />\n不過貓肉味道仲記得，好騷，同羊肉差唔多，但羊肉大大舊，又平，貓肉細細啖，好貴，食貓肉不如食羊肉<br />\n<br />\n當時江門市郊區少少的地方有個貓肉市集，有好多鐵籠困住d貓，俾錢檔主買貓肉後，檔主將隻生勾勾的貓掉落裝滿滾水的大膠桶淥死佢，期間桶內傳出貓隻凄厲的叫聲。淥死左之後撈返上黎用火槍燒毛去貓毛。唔知家陣仲有冇貓肉市集<br />\n<br />\n同埋中醫虎骨係薬材，唔知用貓骨代替得唔得<br />\n<br />\n同埋以前江門有間專食蛇肉的著名食肆叫蛇王南</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你老母俾狗中出"},{"pid":"ed52feec200c1a97dc1843799a20837bdc7c46cc","tid":10732,"uid":20890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:39:20.000Z","msg":"羊肉都已經唔敢食,貓肉狗肉點撚樣食得落"},{"pid":"32583df6d5e94bd9146256aab135c215b71b15e4","tid":10732,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:39:40.000Z","msg":"估唔到呢度有人食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f119ca376402aa55ff01c5ef338025f8c1b37e0","tid":10732,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"只有支那呢d賤種先會又食貓又食狗，仲要當左美食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9438c79d7ed9e2c19d9ee77aa5b7f1cb81d69dd6","tid":10732,"uid":10890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次聽人姓水</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n少人姓但有 中學有個師兄都係姓水"},{"pid":"e845d38d8653d0a46e4c912da85076429e544a2d","tid":10732,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:50:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老實講，狗肉同蛇肉的味道已經唔記得，畢竟好耐之前<br />\n<br />\n不過貓肉味道仲記得，好騷，同羊肉差唔多，但羊肉大大舊，又平，貓肉細細啖，好貴，食貓肉不如食羊肉<br />\n<br />\n當時江門市郊區少少的地方有個貓肉市集，有好多鐵籠困住d貓，俾錢檔主買貓肉後，檔主將隻生勾勾的貓掉落裝滿滾水的大膠桶淥死佢，期間桶內傳出貓隻凄厲的叫聲。淥死左之後撈返上黎用火槍燒毛去貓毛。唔知家陣仲有冇貓肉市集<br />\n<br />\n同埋中醫虎骨係薬材，唔知用貓骨代替得唔得<br />\n<br />\n同埋以前江門有間專食蛇肉的著名食肆叫蛇王南</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸人個種特別賤鳩格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30d43992334641555235da57543822b65224aea","tid":10732,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T05:51:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7faebb042c5bb7a07c4e12db5ca64df9d89b00ea","tid":10732,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:08:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母罰一千， 一大班人夾份食貓狗都得啦冇撚嘢下嘩， 再唔係我請吖"},{"pid":"ce3c28b9a7160896492c3ccc7bd011366ccba816","tid":10732,"uid":27663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:18:31.000Z","msg":"又黎食狗肉食貓肉大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a180a07559e9dba759db4f31d76d9e930c8f4ec3","tid":10732,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:25:27.000Z","msg":"睇左水菜麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a58868047c8a9a99541977634e8c97ccb3702b4","tid":10732,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:26:46.000Z","msg":"又可以釋法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69502415005c8b162adec47d8740b954266b2f60","tid":10732,"uid":349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:06:33.000Z","msg":"違反過逗留條件有案底點解可以入返黎"},{"pid":"0efe6a0c71f10c9a6b7c79381837c5db0b73689b","tid":10732,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:09:54.000Z","msg":"罰得果一千叫尊重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3248f1105a2521b6619307c5593ad32a042a15ad","tid":10732,"uid":33568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:11:22.000Z","msg":"個人覺得食得牛豬雞唔食得貓狗係幾偽善<br />\n不過問題係呢到係香港 有香港既法律<br />\n同埋佢話佢養左隻貓咁耐 整黎食真係好冇人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcde47a636ff846939999bd8dc6c53046ed6d20","tid":10732,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73eef14f552f1642c646149522d8c3fcdccdf9c6","tid":10732,"uid":35657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"大陸人應該滅種<br />\n依啲咁落後既思想"},{"pid":"2017a4e94441cb4b476fc4c02ed489016a87f28f","tid":10732,"uid":7391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:19:27.000Z","msg":"佢老豆死左都可以煮黎食"}]}